des:
Alpha2EQ is the only active biologic therapy created specifically for equine to fight lameness, osteoarthritis, and pain at the source to maximize your horse’s longevity.

Description: Alpha2EQ is the result of years of research to unlock the healing powers of the Alpha-2 Macroglobulin molecule to create a clinically proven, single-treatment biologic therapy that decreases inflammation, relieves pain and treats degeneration of joints in horses. Created by animal lovers, Alpha2EQ harnesses the regenerative and anti-inflammatory properties of the horse’s own blood cells in a treatment that is drug-free and provides no harmful side effects.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
